                     <interp inst="t18180909-64-person570" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Mr. Simpson alarmed me, the prisoner was brought to me with the gingham.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A man told me to wrap it up in my apron.</p>
